quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  51,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  51,1,bakhernay valyon ki qasam jo urra kar bekhair deti hain
  51,2,phir ( pani ka ) boojh athati hain
  51,3,phir aahista aahista chalti hain
  51,4,phir cheeze taqseem karti hain
  51,5,ke jis cheez ka tum se wadakiya jata hai woh sacha hai
  51,6,aur insaaf ( ka din ) zaroor waqay hoga
  51,7,aur aasman ki qasam jis mein rassay hain
  51,8,ke ( ae ahal mecca ) tum aik mutanaqiz (iktalafi) baat mein ( parre hue ) ho
  51,9,is se wohi phirta hai jo ( khuda ki taraf se ) phera jaye
  51,10,atkal doranay walay halaak hon
  51,11,jo be khaberi mein bhoolay hue hain
  51,12,puchhte hain ke jaza ka din kab hoga ?
  51,13,uss din ( hoga ) jab un ko aag mein azaab diya jaye ga
  51,14,ab apni shararat ka maza chako. yeh wohi hai jis ke liye tum jaldi machaya karte they
  51,15,be shak parhaizgaar bahishtoon aur chashmo mein ( aish kar rahay ) hon ge
  51,16,aur ) jo jo ( naematain ) un ka perwar-digaar inhen deta hoga un ko le rahay hon ge. be shak woh is se pehlay naikian karte they
  51,17,raat ke thoray se hissay mein sotay they
  51,18,aur auqaat sehar mein bakhshish manga karte they
  51,19,aur un ke maal mein mangnay walay aur nah mangnay walay ( dono ) ka haq hota tha
  51,20,aur yaqeen karne walon ke liye zameen mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  51,21,aur khud tumahray nafoos mein tokiya tum dekhte nahi ?
  51,22,aur tumhara rizaq aur jis cheez ka tum se wadakiya jata hai aasman mein hai
  51,23,to asmano aur zameen ke maalik ki qasam! yeh ( isi terhan ) qabil yaqeen hai jis terhan tum baat karte ho
  51,24,bhala tumahray paas ibrahim ke Muaziz mehmanon ki khabar pohanchi hai ?
  51,25,jab woh un ke paas aeye to salam kaha. unhon ne bhi ( jawab mein ) salam kaha ( dekha to ) aisay log ke nah jaan nah pehchan
  51,26,to apne ghar ja kar aik ( bhana howa ) mota bitchrha laaye
  51,27,( aur khanay ke liye ) un ke agay rakh diya. kehnay lagey ke aap tanawal kyun nahi karte ?
  51,28,aur dil mein un se khauf maloomkiya. ( unhon ne ) kaha ke khauf nah kijiye. aur un ko aik danishmand larke ki basharat bhi sunai
  51,29,to ibrahim ki biwi chalati aayi aur apna munh pait kar kehnay lagi ke ( ae hai aik to ) budiya aur ( dosray ) banjh
  51,30,( unhon ne ) kaha ( haan ) tumahray perwar-digaar ne yun hi farmaya hai. woh be shak sahib hikmat ( aur ) khabardaar hai
  51,31,ibrahim ne kaha ke farishto! tumhara muddakiya hai ?
  51,32,unhon ne kaha ke hum gunehgaar logon ki taraf beje gay hain
  51,33,taakay un par khangar barsaaen
  51,34,jin par hadd se barh jaane walon ke liye tumahray perwar-digaar ke haan se nishaan kardiye gay hain
  51,35,to wahan jitne momin they un ko hum ne nikaal liya
  51,36,aur is mein aik ghar ke siwa musalmanoon ka koi ghar nah paaya
  51,37,aur jo log azaab alim se drtay hain un ke liye wahan nishani chore di
  51,38,aur moose ( ke haal ) mein ( bhi nishani hai ) jab hum ne un ko firaon ki taraf khula howa moujza day kar bheja
  51,39,to is ne apni jamaat ( ke ghamand ) par munh mourr liya aur kehnay laga yeh to jadugar hai ya deewana
  51,40,to hum ne is ko aur is ke lashkaron ko pakar liya aur un ko darya mein pheink diya aur woh kaam hi qabil malamat karta tha
  51,41,aur Aad ( ki qoum ke haal ) mein bhi ( nishani hai ) jab hum ne un par namubarak howa chalaye
  51,42,woh jis cheez par chalti is ko rezah rezah kiye baghair nah chodthee
  51,43,aur ( qoum ) smod ( ke haal ) mein ( nishani hai ) jab un se kaha gaya ke aik waqt taq faida utha lo
  51,44,to unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se sar kashi ki. so un ko kadak ne aa pakra aur woh dekh rahay they
  51,45,phir woh nah to utney ki taaqat rakhtay they aur nah muqaabla hi kar saktay they
  51,46,aur is se pehlay ( hum ) Nooh ki qoum ko ( halaak kar chukay they ) be shak woh nafarman log they
  51,47,aur asmano ko hum hi ne hathon se banaya aur hum ko sab Maqdoor hai
  51,48,aur zameen ko hum hi ne bichhaya to ( dekho ) humkiya khoob bichenay walay hain
  51,49,aur har cheez ki hum ne do kasmain banayen taakay tum nasiyaat pakro
  51,50,to tum log khuda ki taraf bhaag chalo mein is ki taraf se tum ko Sarih rasta bitanay wala hon
  51,51,aur khuda ke sath kisi aur ko mabood nah banaao. mein is ki taraf se tum ko Sarih rasta bitanay wala hon
  51,52,isi terhan un se pehlay logon ke paas jo paighambar aata woh is ko jadugar ya deewana kehte
  51,53,kiya yeh ke aik dosray ko isi baat ki wasiyat karte aeye hain balkay yeh shareer log hain
  51,54,to un se aaraiz karo. tum ko ( hamari ) taraf se malamat nah hogi
  51,55,aur nasiyaat karte raho ke nasiyaat mominoun ko naffa deti hai
  51,56,aur mein ne junoo aur insanon ko is liye pedakiya hai ke meri ibadat karen
  51,57,mein un se taalib rizaq nahi aur nah yeh chahta hon ke mujhe ( khana ) khilain
  51,58,khuda hi to rizaq dainay wala zor aawar aur mazboot hai
  51,59,kuch shak nahi ke un zaalmon ke liye bhi ( azaab ki ) nobat muqarrar hai jis terhan un ke sathiyon ki nobat thi to un ko mujh se ( azaab ) jaldi nahi talab karna chahiye
  51,60,jis din ka un kafiroon se wadakiya jata hai is se un ke liye kharabi hai
